Package: tcgsaseq
Type: Package
Title: Time-Course Gene Set Analysis for RNA-Seq Data
Version: 1.6.1
Date: 2017-08-04
Authors@R: c(person("Denis", "Agniel", role = c("aut"),
                    email = "denis.agniel@gmail.com"),
	           person("Boris P.", "Hejblum", role = c("aut", "cre"),
	                  email = "boris.hejblum@u-bordeaux.fr"))
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.2)
Imports:
    CompQuadForm,
    ggplot2,
    GSA,
    KernSmooth,
    stats,
    utils
Suggests:
    limma,
    edgeR,
    DESeq2,
    S4Vectors,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
biocViews: DifferentialExpression, GeneExpression, RNASeq, Sequencing, Software, 
    StatisticalMethod, SystemsBiology, TimeCourse, Transcriptomics
Description: Analysis of RNA-seq data with variance component score test accounting 
    for data heteroscedasticity through precision weights. Perform both gene-wise and gene set
    analyses and can deal with longitudinal data. Method is detailed in: Agniel D, Hejblum BP (2017) 
    Variance component score test for time-course gene set analysis of longitudinal RNA-seq data, Biostatistics. 
    <arXiv:1605.02351>
LazyData: true
